Table C_PIB_LOCATION_HISTORY

Card of table C_PIB_LOCATION_HISTORY

Name

C_PIB_LOCATION_HISTORY


Description of the table C_PIB_LOCATION_HISTORY

20-Nov-2022

 

History of changes to Functional Location related to Equipment.

 

Source: CDHDR/CDPOS

Changes in ILOA Account Assignment Number are tracked, ILOA number is used to get the Functional Location, ILOA Account Assignment Number may change but Functional Location is not change.

 

RECORD_START_DATE to RECORD_END_DATE has the Equipment number and LOCATION_ID (Functional Location) that was assigned during that time period.

 

Current Truth/Functional Location on th equipment, IS_ACTIVE = Y

If the current value of the Functional Location location on the equipment has been changed to null/deleted then IS_LAST_VERSION = Y and IS_DELETED = Y

 

Update Frequency: Daily UDATE and UTIME changes.
